</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="1.[264,1323,1318,1905]" pageId="1">Unfortunately the quality of the photos is not optimal due to the quality of the specimen.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="1.[264,1323,1318,1905]" pageId="1">
<bibRefCitation author="Horning, D. S. &amp; Schuster, R. O. &amp; Grigarick, A. A." box="[312,567,1479,1505]" pageId="1" pagination="185 - 280" refId="ref4789" refString="Horning, D. S., Schuster, R. O. &amp; Grigarick, A. A. (1978) Tardigrada from New Zealand. New Zealand Journal of Zoology, 5, 185 - 280." type="journal article" year="1978">
